BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Colour by Number
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260331T153000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260331T163000
UID:699cf21ecbf6405d356866b8@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Colour by Numbers is an interactive colouring activity. It is 
 designed to improve your number recognition skills as you have fun with co
 lours.\nJoin us in this relaxing program and feel your artistic spirit. Th
 e most important thing is you do not have to use your brain\, just do it.\
 nAll ages. Drop-in\, No registration required.
