UID:69b2e1f71e64afd01e619f49@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Join us for visits with a therapy dog. Children will have an o
 pportunity to read\, listen to stories\, and engage in therapeutic human-a
 nimal interaction.   Children who live with a disability\, are neurodiverg
 ent\, or have experienced medical or other types of trauma are especially 
 welcome.\nThis program is presented in partnership with One Health Partner
 s.\nDrop-in\, no registration required.
LOCATION:Runnymede\, Children's Area
