DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260409T200000
UID:69b9e3e267801235ed72c6dc@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:In this advanced workshop participants will be taken step by s
 tep through creating a still life digital painting from a photo reference
  in Adobe Photoshop. We will be using a Wacom drawing tablet. The instruct
 or will touch base on important art principles relating to form\, that wil
 l be applied to painting in Adobe Photoshop.\nPrior experience with drawin
 g tablets and Photoshop is required for this class. Though\, we will brief
 ly go over the user interface and various tools we will be using. If you a
 re looking for an introduction class or an in depth look at the broader a
 spects of Photoshop please look out for our\nDigital Painting I: Introduct
 ion & Pen Control\nor\nIntroduction to Photo Editing in Photoshop\nprogram
 s.\nFor more information about this program please contact dihonline@tpl.c
 a.
